text: You're telling me! We have 5 people in the house so she's rarely alone,  I just want to spend more time with her!  I work 2 jobs and go to college

Actually its a lot,  my study will be getting people to recognize how we can connect our mental,  sexual and psychological all together instead of thinking of them as separate entities.  I also want to be an intimacy coach, for all people.  Nothing like a marriage coach.
